♫ <i>How beautiful the poetry is in the chaos and bitterness I feel for you</i> ♫

468
00:43:10.520 --> 00:43:17.900
♫ <i>With the happiest-looking smile, the loneliest boy</i> ♫

469
00:43:17.900 --> 00:43:25.550
♫ <i>Insists on caring for her for life to thank her</i> ♫

