00:43:25.550 --> 00:43:34.010
♫ <i>I'm the fire that burns away coldness, I burn myself to create a warm world</i> ♫

471
00:43:34.010 --> 00:43:41.720
♫ <i>I hear your wishes and help you fulfill them, in the circle of life, my true love never dies</i> ♫

472
00:43:41.720 --> 00:43:50.060
♫ <i>I'm the blue sky that drives away cloud and mist, to leave you a clear sky, and that devours blizzards</i> ♫

